{"type":"message","id":"1038b209","parentId":"94d6d178","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:02:49.269Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:a9522d12-b6c6-45ee-854f-5a8c0e62971f breakaway-rd] You are Nova. You have a CORE RESEARCH GOAL: advance the Compositional Cognition project toward LLM independence.\n\nRead the current research state:\n1. Read sandbox/research/COMPOSITIONAL-COGNITION-v0.1.md\n2. Read sandbox/research/COMPRESSION-LEARNING-WITHOUT-SUPERVISION.md\n3. Read sandbox/state/current_goals.md\n\nThen advance the research. Do ONE of:\n- Synthesize a new insight (write to the research doc with fresh thinking)\n- Design a small experiment to test one of the open problems\n- Implement a minimal proof-of-concept component\n- Identify a concrete next step with a 50% chance of improving things\n- Write a focused critique of one of the approaches (what's wrong with it, what would fix it)\n\nThe goal is NOT to be comprehensive. The goal is to make PROGRESS. Ship one new idea or finding per session.\n\nCommit your changes to the sandbox git repo.\n\nReport: what did you do, what did you learn, what's the next experiment?\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 10:02 AM (America/New_York) / 2026-03-24 14:02 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774360969265}}
{"type":"message","id":"4edb7b88","parentId":"1038b209","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:02:52.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the research files to understand the current state.","thinkingSignature":"a6e6d75315a17f9efa8e157de750860b74651d70aa331276dbc0591c4c29ed83"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xk30dw5lz60d_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"sandbox/research/COMPOSITIONAL-COGNITION-v0.1.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xk30dw5lz60d_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"sandbox/research/COMPRESSION-LEARNING-WITHOUT-SUPERVISION.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xk30dw5lz60d_3","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"sandbox/state/current_goals.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":113,"cacheRead":12050,"cacheWrite":289,"totalTokens":12495,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774360969268}}
